Package com.library.database.entities

Class Reader

java.lang.Object
com.library.database.entities.Reader
All Implemented Interfaces:
DBEntity
@Entity public class Reader extends Object implements DBEntity
The Reader class represents a library reader with personal information, contact details, and a list of associated book forms. It also includes a reader rating.

This class is annotated with JPA annotations for entity mapping and is designed to be used with a relational database.
